      <title>香港拟提议禁止电子烟，并对公共场所吸烟实施新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hong-kong-to-propose-ban-on-vaping-new-curbs-on-public-smoking</link>
